design and training services for pharmaceutical and medical research organizations, biotech companies, medical academia, and continuing medical
education organizations. Services include: investigator training program including a comprehensive manual; educational presentations; clinical study
management issues including subject/patient safety, inclusion/exclusion criteria, and special population study matters; assessment of study sites;
design and evaluation of research protocols; representation on safety boards, medical consultants, IRB�s, planning committees and Boards of Directors; choice
of surrogate and pharmacodynamic markers; asthma management and protocol advice; educational presentations; and training of pharmaceutical
representatives from a practice perspective. All services are in a GCP committed and comfortable manner">
